Formula 1 ace Lewis Hamilton boasts about flying his pet pooches all around the world in a private jet – despite also claiming to be a vegan in a bid to make the world a better place.
Most recently the current F1 champion said he flies his bulldog Coco from his home in Malibu, California so it can catch up with Roscoe – the same breed – who prefers life in the UK.
Hamilton, 34, posted a picture of Coco on a private jet, adding: ‘In case you didn’t know about my two kids.
